      var offset = (this.currentPage - 1)*this.typePage + 1 ;
      const response = await axios.get(
        "http://localhost:55810/api/Products/Paginate?offset="+ offset +"&limit="+ this.typePage+"&sellPrice=0&isShow=2&status=2"
      );

    },
